Subject: [PATCH] ppu/include: <cell/sysutil_gamecontent.h> cell-SDK-source compat

Fifth the backfill workstream SDK header.  Same cell-SDK-source-compat pattern as
psl1ght/0014 (savedata): cell-SDK struct types with cell-SDK field names,
cell-SDK callback typedefs, cell-SDK enum surface, forwarders that cast
pointers to PSL1GHT's sysGame* types and delegate.

Covers:
  - CellGameContentSize, CellGameSetInitParams (layout pinned via
    _Static_assert to PSL1GHT's sysGame* equivalents).
  - CellGameDiscEjectCallback, CellGameDiscInsertCallback,
    CellGameThemeInstallCallback.
  - CELL_GAME_RET_OK / _CANCEL / _NONE, 18 error codes.
  - CELL_GAME_GAMETYPE_SYS / DISC / HDD / GAMEDATA / HOME.
  - CELL_GAME_ATTRIBUTE_* (PATCH / APP_HOME / DEBUG / XMBBUY /
    COMMERCE2_BROWSER / INVITE_MESSAGE / CUSTOM_DATA_MESSAGE /
    WEB_BROWSER).
  - CELL_GAME_THEME_OPTION_*, CELL_GAME_CBRESULT_*.
  - CELL_GAME_SYSP_* sizes.
  - CELL_GAME_PARAMID_* full enum (TITLE + per-language variants,
    TITLE_ID / VERSION / PARENTAL_LEVEL / RESOLUTION / SOUND_FORMAT /
    PS3_SYSTEM_VER / APP_VER).
  - CELL_GAME_ERRDIALOG_*, CELL_GAME_RESOLUTION_*,
    CELL_GAME_SOUNDFORMAT_*, CELL_GAME_DISCTYPE_*.
  - 17 function forwarders: cellGameDataCheck, BootCheck,
    PatchCheck, CreateGameData, GetParamInt, GetParamString,
    GetSizeKB, SetParamString, GetDiscContentInfoUpdatePath,
    ContentPermit, ContentErrorDialog, ThemeInstall,
    ThemeInstallFromBuffer, GetLocalWebContentPath, DeleteGameData,
    RegisterDiscChangeCallback, UnregisterDiscChangeCallback.

Verified: samples/hello-ppu-gamedata ELF imports cell-SDK FNIDs
0xf52639ea, 0x42a2e133, 0xdb9819f3, 0x70acec67, 0xb7a45caf,
0x3a5d726a — all present in .rodata.sceFNID as expected.

New sample samples/hello-ppu-gamedata exercises cellGameBootCheck
+ cellGameContentPermit + cellGameGetParamString + GetParamInt to
probe how the running app was launched, its PARAM.SFO, parental
level, etc.  Build green.

diff --git a/ppu/include/cell/sysutil_gamecontent.h b/ppu/include/cell/sysutil_gamecontent.h
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..45c2c29
--- /dev/null
+++ b/ppu/include/cell/sysutil_gamecontent.h
@@ -0,0 +1,303 @@
+/*! \file cell/sysutil_gamecontent.h
+ \brief cell-SDK-source-compat cellGame* API — the backfill workstream forwarder.
+
+  the reference sysutil_gamecontent.h + sysutil_game_common.h surface over
+  PSL1GHT's libsysutil.a (which embeds cell-SDK FNIDs under renamed
+  sysGame* wrappers).  Source written against the reference cell-SDK headers
+  compiles unchanged against this header.
+
+  Verified FNIDs imported by user code:
+    cellGameBootCheck                     0xf52639ea
+    cellGameDataCheck                     0xdb9819f3
+    cellGamePatchCheck                    0xf8115d69
+    cellGameCreateGameData                0x42a2e133
+    cellGameGetParamInt                   0xb7a45caf
+    cellGameGetParamString                0x3a5d726a
+    cellGameGetSizeKB                     0xef9d42d5
+    cellGameSetParamString                0xdaa5cd20
+    cellGameGetDiscContentInfoUpdatePath  0x2a8e6b92
+    cellGameContentPermit                 0x70acec67
+    cellGameContentErrorDialog            0xb0a1f8c6
+    cellGameThemeInstall                  0xd24e3928
+    cellGameThemeInstallFromBuffer        0x87406734
+    cellGameGetLocalWebContentPath        0xa80bf223
+    cellGameDeleteGameData                0xb367c6e3
+    cellGameRegisterDiscChangeCallback    0xef9d42d5
+    cellGameUnregisterDiscChangeCallback  0x3e22cb4b
+*/
+
+#ifndef __PSL1GHT_CELL_SYSUTIL_GAMECONTENT_H__
+#define __PSL1GHT_CELL_SYSUTIL_GAMECONTENT_H__
+
+#include <sysutil/game.h>
+#include <ppu-types.h>
+
+#ifdef __cplusplus
+extern "C" {
+#endif
